   About section (like shophia website page)

Ingredient Commitment
At EXOVITA, we believe true care begins with simplicity and purity.
Our products are crafted using traditional Ayurvedic herbs and natural botanicals, blended thoughtfully with pure coconut oil as our base. Every ingredient is chosen with care, respecting ancient wisdom and modern quality standards.
Key ingredients we use include:
•	Amla (Indian Gooseberry) 
•	Bhringraj 
•	Brahmi 
•	Neem 
•	Hibiscus 
•	Aloe Vera 
•	Pure Coconut Oil 
We do not use harsh chemicals, parabens, sulfates, or artificial colors. Every EXOVITA product is made with honesty, care, and respect for nature.

Why Use Ayurvedic Hair Oil & Soap?
Ayurveda believes that true beauty comes from balance, not quick fixes.
Ayurvedic Hair Oil
Ayurvedic hair oil works by nourishing the scalp and hair at the root level, using herbs and natural ingredients that have been trusted for centuries. Unlike chemical-based products that give temporary results, Ayurvedic oils focus on long-term hair health.
Benefits of Ayurvedic hair oil:
•	Strengthens hair roots and reduces hair fall
•	Improves scalp health and circulation
•	Supports natural hair growth
•	Helps reduce dryness, dandruff, and breakage
•	Promotes thicker, healthier-looking hair over time
Regular oiling is considered a self-care ritual in Ayurveda, helping maintain balance and overall wellness.
________________________________________
Ayurvedic Handmade Soap
Ayurvedic soaps are made with natural ingredients that cleanse the skin gently without stripping away its natural moisture. They work in harmony with the skin rather than against it.
Benefits of Ayurvedic handmade soap:
•	Cleanses skin without causing dryness or irritation
•	Helps maintain the skin’s natural moisture balance
•	Suitable for all skin types, including sensitive skin
•	Supports healthy, glowing skin with regular use
•	Free from harsh chemicals and synthetic additives
Ayurvedic soaps turn daily cleansing into a mindful ritual of care and nourishment.
________________________________________
By choosing Ayurvedic hair oil and soap, you choose natural care, time-tested wisdom, and gentle effectiveness — a return to purity, balance, and wellness.

Privacy Policy section 
At EXOVITA, your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you visit or interact with our website.
By using our website, you agree to the practices described in this policy.
________________________________________
Information We Collect
When you visit or use our website, we may collect the following information:
•	Personal details such as name, email address, phone number, and shipping address when you place an order or contact us
•	Payment-related information (processed securely through trusted third-party payment gateways)
•	Basic technical information such as IP address, browser type, and device data for website performance and security
We only collect information that is necessary to provide our services and improve your experience.
________________________________________
How We Use Your Information
The information we collect is used to:
•	Process and deliver your orders
•	Communicate with you about orders, support, or updates
•	Improve our products, services, and website experience
•	Send promotional emails or offers (only if you choose to receive them)
We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to third parties.
________________________________________
Data Protection & Security
We take reasonable steps to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, misuse, or disclosure. Your data is stored securely, and all transactions are handled through trusted and secure systems.
However, please note that no method of online transmission is 100% secure.
________________________________________
Cookies
Our website may use cookies to enhance your browsing experience. Cookies help us understand how visitors use our site and allow us to improve functionality. You can choose to disable cookies through your browser settings if you prefer.
________________________________________
Third-Party Services
We may use third-party services (such as payment gateways or delivery partners) to complete transactions and deliver products. These third parties have their own privacy policies, and we recommend reviewing them separately.
________________________________________
Your Rights
You have the right to:
•	Access or update your personal information
•	Request deletion of your data (subject to legal or operational requirements)
•	Opt out of promotional communications at any time
For any privacy-related requests, you can contact us directly.
________________________________________
Changes to This Policy
EXOVITA reserves the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated effective date.


Shipping Information
At EXOVITA, we aim to deliver your products safely and on time. To ensure reliable and efficient delivery, we have partnered with Shiprocket, a trusted shipping and logistics platform.
________________________________________
Shipping Partner
All orders placed on our website are shipped through Shiprocket, which works with multiple courier partners to provide timely and secure delivery across India.
________________________________________
Order Processing Time
•	Orders are usually processed within 1–3 business days after order confirmation.
•	Orders placed on Sundays or public holidays will be processed on the next working day.
________________________________________
Delivery Time
•	Estimated delivery time is 3–7 business days, depending on your location.
•	Delivery timelines may vary due to weather conditions, courier delays, or regional restrictions.
________________________________________
Shipping Charges
•	Shipping charges (if applicable) will be clearly mentioned at checkout before payment.
•	Any free shipping offers will be applied automatically.
________________________________________
Order Tracking
Once your order is shipped, you will receive a tracking link via SMS or email from Shiprocket, allowing you to monitor your delivery status in real time.
________________________________________
Delivery Address
Please ensure that your shipping address, contact number, and pin code are accurate at the time of placing the order. EXOVITA is not responsible for delays or non-delivery due to incorrect information provided by the customer.
________________________________________
Damaged or Missing Packages
If your package arrives damaged or incomplete, please contact us within 48 hours of delivery with clear images and order details so we can assist you promptly.

